1
00:01:00,250 --> 00:01:04,333
Based on the short story by Moreira Campos
故事出自於Moreira Campos

2
00:01:19,583 --> 00:01:24,041
Dogs are Said to See Things
狗目睹了一切

3
00:02:47,541 --> 00:02:48,625
Yeah!
對！

4
00:02:49,291 --> 00:02:50,916
Yes, it's close.
恩，很接近了

5
00:02:50,916 --> 00:02:52,666
How close?
有多近了？

6
00:02:52,666 --> 00:02:55,708
Well, can't you feel the heat?
恩，你們沒有感覺到那熱氣嗎？

7
00:03:14,833 --> 00:03:19,125
So that the sky might turn blue
那天空可能會變藍

8
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:24,291
So that the planet might be one
而那星球也將成為其中之一

9
00:03:25,083 --> 00:03:27,083
And mankind...
而人類…

10
00:03:34,833 --> 00:03:37,416
See how he likes that?  Can't you see?
你們看他有多喜歡？ 看不出來嗎？

11
00:03:37,416 --> 00:03:39,791
He's really enjoying it.
他真的很享受

12
00:03:40,291 --> 00:03:42,083
- It's me?  - No.
- 我的？ - 不是

13
00:03:44,291 --> 00:03:45,166
Hey...
嘿…

14
00:03:45,625 --> 00:03:48,750
...take that stuff off my face, damn it! Shit!
把那東西從我臉上移開，該死的！媽的！

15
00:04:56,458 --> 00:04:58,416
Asshole!
混蛋！

16
00:05:22,375 --> 00:05:23,875
Attention everyone!
各位注意一下！

17
00:05:23,875 --> 00:05:26,416
Lunch is served!
中餐可以開始享用了！

18
00:05:28,125 --> 00:05:31,208
Hey, get to the back of the line!
嘿，到後面排隊去！

19
00:05:32,375 --> 00:05:34,583
What if you meet someone?
要是你遇見了甚麼人呢？

20
00:05:34,583 --> 00:05:35,563
We never know.
世事難料

21
00:05:35,663 --> 00:05:37,999
Yes, it's better to be prepared.
對呀，最好先有心理準備

22
00:05:38,750 --> 00:05:40,541
- Have a nice meal.  - Thanks.
- 祝你用餐愉快  - 謝謝

23
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:48,166
- Come here, get in. Come on!  - Thanks.
- 來呀，排這。來嘛！  - 謝了

24
00:05:48,166 --> 00:05:51,416
After all, you're growing up girl.
畢竟，妳也在發育嘛

25
00:11:01,708 --> 00:11:04,450
I wouldn't miss you at all
我一點都不會想你

26
00:11:04,550 --> 00:11:08,249
on a sunny sunday at Beach Park
在海灘公園 一個晴朗的星期天

27
00:11:08,250 --> 00:11:11,416
There's no way I would take you along
我是不可能帶你

28
00:11:11,516 --> 00:11:15,040
for a walk with me at Iguatemi Mall.
一起逛Iguatemi商場

29
00:11:15,041 --> 00:11:18,094
I wouldn't dare facing the embarrassment
我無法面對被

30
00:11:18,194 --> 00:11:22,040
in front of my cool friends from Aldeota.
那些自Aldeota朋友發現的窘境

31
00:11:22,041 --> 00:11:25,555
Because now I hold a high reputation
因為我在現在的社交圈裡

32
00:11:25,655 --> 00:11:29,832
among the high circles of high society.
有一定的地位

33
00:11:29,833 --> 00:11:33,565
I know that the bourgeoisie stinks
雖然我知道那資產階級的腐敗

34
00:11:33,665 --> 00:11:37,082
but it has money to buy perfume.
但那讓我有錢得到我要的

35
00:11:37,083 --> 00:11:39,800
What's more, in the high society
再者，在這資本社會裡

36
00:11:39,900 --> 00:11:43,582
people are cheated on without getting jealous.
人們毫無理由的互相欺騙

37
00:11:43,583 --> 00:11:47,185
I know that the bourgeoisie stinks
雖然我知道那資產階級的腐敗

38
00:11:47,285 --> 00:11:50,582
but it has money to buy perfume.
但那讓我有錢得到我要的

39
00:12:03,750 --> 00:12:08,628
I'm IN, I'm not OUT.
我身陷其中，不像你是局外人

40
